1. clone repository : git clone https://github.com/<username>/<repo-name>.git

go inside folder : 
cd <repo-name>

2. modify file : 
echo "Updated content" >> README.md

3. view updated files : 
cat README.md

4. see changes : 
git diff

5. Commit and push : 
add file : 
git add README.md

commit changes: 
git commit -m "docs: update README with new content"

push to github: 
git push origin main

check commits : 
git log --oneline -3


